{"tid":716361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"墨西哥市長候選人遭槍殺 疑犯竟是當地28名警察","createTime":"2018-06-25T07:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T04:16:34.000Z","uid":75969,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5d23febd2838fb95b98c8bb4429f138378f37770","tid":716361,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180625/_2018062515435275033.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180625%2F_2018062515435275033.jpg&h=ef1c7c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">28名警員涉與Fernando &Aacute;ngeles Ju&aacute;rez被殺案有關。網圖<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥米卻肯州奧坎波市 (Ocampo) 市長候選人Fernando &Aacute;ngeles Ju&aacute;rez，近日在家外被槍殺。當局調查後發現，當地警局全體28名警員有重大嫌疑，已將他們全數拘留調查。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》報道，墨西哥政府於24日發表聲明，透露奧坎波市警察局的所有成員都被警方內政部門調查，並集中調查可能違反警方準則的行為，但沒有提供更多細節。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，墨西哥於7月1日舉行大選前，至今已有百多名政治人物被殺害，Fernando &Aacute;ngeles Ju&aacute;rez更是米卻肯州於一周內第3名死亡的政治人物。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/749542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F749542&d=2cyo8dFeyNMIOGkW81WWsr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=49e7b8d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F749542&h=0a4835a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/749542</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前個18歲美女候選人會唔會被輪大米<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50334216375da29cb26ce05d9aa83116a478ef28","tid":716361,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T08:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513df438bdc75de6ec0c0fcb8c6ef6d31ba679b6","tid":716361,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":